{
  "texts": [
    "We store all generated metadata in a duckdb database (Mühleisen",
    "articles PK article_id VARCHAR year UINT FK source VARCHAR title VARCHAR content_hash VARCHAR publication_date DATE FK topic_id UINT url VARCHAR covid_article BOOL sources PK source VARCHAR url VARCHAR label ENUM bias ENUM factuality ENUM country VARCHAR type VARCHAR popularity ENUM credibility ENUM reasoning VARCHAR conspiracy ENUM pseudosci ENUM check_date DATE topics PK topic_id UINT year UINT representation VARCHAR imbalanced_hyper_cluste UINT balanced_hyper_cluster UINT Figure B.1 Schema for the generated metadata database.",
    "'PK' indicates primary key, 'FK' denotes a foreign key relationship.",
    "and Raasveldt 2024).",
    "Figure B.1 depicts the metadata schema."
  ]
}